00:02:57.550 --> 00:02:59.049
I want you to develop
some intuition

00:02:59.049 --> 00:03:00.710
for quantum phenomena.

00:03:00.710 --> 00:03:03.400
Now, quantam
mechanics is not hard.

00:03:03.400 --> 00:03:05.875
It has a reputation
for being a hard topic.

00:03:05.875 --> 00:03:07.585
It is not a super hard topic.

00:03:10.460 --> 00:03:12.280
