other in the sense

00:30:36.000 --> 00:30:41.170
not that you can't know, because
you can't know whether it's

00:30:41.170 --> 00:30:43.450
hard and soft
simultaneously, deeper.

00:30:43.450 --> 00:30:47.690
It is not hard and
white simultaneously.

00:30:47.690 --> 00:30:48.600
It cannot be.

00:30:48.600 --> 00:30:50.580
It does not mean
anything to say it

00:30:50.580 --> 00:30:54.770
is hard and white
simultaneously.

00:30:54.770 --> 00:30:56.270
That is uncertainty.

00:30:56.270 --> 00:30:58.290
